19#include "Point.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22
23/**
24* <p>Encapsulates a point of interest in an image containing a barcode. Typically, this
25* would be the location of a finder pattern or the corner of the barcode, for example.</p>
26*
27* @author Sean Owen
28*/
29class ResultPoint : public PointF
30{
31public:
32 ResultPoint() = default;
33 ResultPoint(float x, float y) : PointF(x, y) {}
34 ResultPoint(int x, int y) : PointF(x, y) {}
35 template <typename T> ResultPoint(PointT<T> p) : PointF(p) {}
36
37 float x() const { return static_cast<float>(PointF::x); }
38 float y() const { return static_cast<float>(PointF::y); }
39
40 void set(float x, float y) { *this = PointF(x, y); }
41
42 static float Distance(int aX, int aY, int bX, int bY);
43};
44
45} // ZXing
